{"tid":2127616,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"蘋論：政府要令市民選無可選！ - 盧峯","createTime":"2020-07-27T11:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T12:25:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5085b560f1d4c7f657145106f0897f5caf4a94e7","tid":2127616,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:58:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200727/XPC5SBDCJTRORGU577P7Z65OPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FXPC5SBDCJTRORGU577P7Z65OPQ%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpaRE6aJPUBN7WNjl4CDefRw%3D&h=f509feda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FXPC5SBDCJTRORGU577P7Z65OPQ%2F&h=a06c1de2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200727/XPC5SBDCJTRORGU577P7Z65OPQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n蘋論：政府要令市民選無可選！ - 盧峯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cwV1xZ45BNnA4KGADlLNhRaWvnE=/900x506/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/C5LB4GXMEOK5JNNJMCVLU47HYQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcwV1xZ45BNnA4KGADlLNhRaWvnE%3D%2F900x506%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FC5LB4GXMEOK5JNNJMCVLU47HYQ.gif&h=a7143584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主選舉本是件平常不過的事，就如英國名相邱吉爾所言：「民主的要義是讓平民百姓走進普通不過的票站，用鉛筆在選票上劃上小小的記號（選出代表）」&rdquo;At the bottom of all the tributes paid to democracy is the little man, walking into the little booth, with a little pencil, making a little cross on a little bit of paper&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n可是，對一國兩制已土崩。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無故延選期 欠法理基礎<br />\n<br />\n先說選舉日程。新一屆立法會選舉日期早經憲報公佈為9月6日，提名期則已開始。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n問題是，曾鈺成的建議既缺乏法理基礎，也不符合社會需要，更開創極壞先例，而所。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n武肺疫情。。。。。。。。。。。。減低傳播病毒機會。<br />\n<br />\n投票日的安排同樣可。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n刁難候選人 否決變罪名<br />\n<br />\n除了想在選舉日子上動手腳以外，特區政府還打算把立法會選舉變成北韓式的偽選舉，包括利用選舉主任的權力把民望高又不聽話的候選人排除，甚至把泛民主派候選人大舉DQ，只剩下建制派或面目、立場模糊的候選人入閘出選。這兩天多位泛民主派候選人先後收到選舉主任多個額外問題，例如要求他們解釋以否決預算案為方法逼政府回應訴求如何合乎「擁護《基本法》」、「效忠特區」的要求。<br />\n<br />\n提這些問題的選舉主任。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n今屆選舉即使有候選人提出否。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n盧峯<br />\n周一至周六刊出"},{"pid":"d027a5a9018d86eef91dbc7428d2f2895d1ea6b4","tid":2127616,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"tvb 開工班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算上鏡拍劇<br />\n套劇下年先出街都要戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戴住口罩選港姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa27285f65e7c47001a686b3cbfcb0b5f2e36141","tid":2127616,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:23:57.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707dd007bd5e2256c0ce8144ad6f6e948395a945","tid":2127616,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:25:18.000Z","msg":"推"}]}